str1=input("Enter a string: ");
length=len(str1)
print("No.of characters of the given string",length);
str2=input("Enter a string in lower case letters");
print(str2.upper())
str3=input("Enter a string in upper case letters");
print(str3.lower())
str4=input("Enter a string in both upper and lower case letters: ");
print(str4.swapcase())
output:
Enter a string: kciq
No.of characters of the given string 4
Enter a string in lower case lettersmkmsxmc
MKMSXMC
Enter a string in upper case lettersJDFKXM
jdfkxm
Enter a string in both upper and lower case letters: KImjnjKLnj
kiMJNJklNJ
